---
title: North Indian Style Beef Mince and Pea Curry with Basmati Rice and Cashew Nuts
description: This North Indian Style Beef Mince and Pea Curry is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
